<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir nehst
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Sluttenhof<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell
                        gesant <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> als von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hett, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ir <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        ewch habt <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen, des wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell
                            <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> danken. Denn als ir
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> desmals <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, an uns ze <expan>werbe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir uns mit
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell richten
                            <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                        edel mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir die sache gen uns
                        wellet fallen lassen und auch, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Sluttenhof<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu disem mal an
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel werbe von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir im das
                            <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        von ewch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell wol getrawen. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
